{"tid":1126733,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實劇透係唔係違法? 如果唔違法拉大隊日日去戲院門口劇透所有戲既內容有沒得諗?","createTime":"2019-04-26T14:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T20:50:08.000Z","uid":44748,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9deac93eab38868567b3563d4b9fd1d571d550f6","tid":1126733,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"拉大隊心口掛個牌係身上寫住電影重點劇透內容 <br />\n等班人就算係戲院前帶耳機防劇透都沒用<br />\n你一定望到<br />\n然後當然搵定D好似保標D大隻佬一齊去 <br />\n再唔係就自己練大隻<br />\n一個人就話好似大人蝦細路比人打<br />\n一班人邊個夠膽用暴力打你<br />\n如果又唔違法<br />\n即係法律同暴力都沒用<br />\n怕比人公審?用傳媒力量?<br />\n咁咪帶定面具口罩之類既野唔洗比人認出 又win<br />\n社會上一定有大堆鍾意焦土既人會做呢堆野 例如on9仔<br />\n<br />\n所以有冇波台手足會一齊組個團去戲院/商場周邊行行企企劇透<br />\n<br />\n團員名單暫時有:<br />\n世界色情王(可能係世上界上最好打既笠水王)<br />\nN賓(可能係世上界上最有道德既刺客)<br />\n2和B(可能係世上界上最有性慾既智障人士)<br />\n<br />\n仲有沒人想join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:本人係唔會做呢D野"},{"pid":"6eb968b706c49bbb91aab3b83e021b1f7015a423","tid":1126733,"uid":194525,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"兒登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b66ca158e100133985524298a3587672c8d77d8","tid":1126733,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"幼稚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4def05d2c234960df08c302040957fdffdab52e","tid":1126733,"uid":27939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"2&amp;b個朵真心貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d280d5291880cbf48b7d7f1facfacb9bd9d6e09","tid":1126733,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0